title: #52: One Year w Adderal and Compliments host Annabelle DeSisto and show regular Taylor "The Bare Naked Cucucumber" O'Connor - Listener Call-Ins,  Work Life Relationship Balance, First Job out of College

description:
Lauryn & Michael are celebrating one year of podcasting and taking listener calls. They discuss how to gauge when it's the right time to leave your day-job to go full force into your own business, dealing with anxiety over starting your first job out of college, balancing work life with a relationship, and Annabelle DeSisto host of the podcast "Adderall and Compliments" gives a peek into her date with Taylor the "Bare Naked Cucumber."
